Simple Python Chatbot

This is a basic chatbot implemented in Python using the Tkinter library. It provides a simple text-based interface where users can chat with the bot. The bot responds to basic greetings and questions using predefined responses.

Features:

Simple GUI interface
Basic keyword-based responses
Clear and concise code
How to Use:

Clone the repository:

Bash

git clone https://github.com/Rishiofficial432-432/simple-chatbot
Use code with caution.

Install dependencies:

Bash
cd simple-chatbot
pip install tkinter
Use code with caution.

Run the script:

Bash
python chatbot.py
Use code with caution.

Feel free to customize and extend this chatbot by:

Adding more keywords and responses.
Implementing more complex natural language processing techniques.
Integrating with external APIs for real-time information.
Adding a graphical user interface with a more appealing design.
Enjoy!
